snippet.textDisplay: Three years back, me and a group of colleagues were having dinner at a dhaba on Haryana Rajasthan border, a folk singer was singing Kesariya Balama outside the dhaba. It was almost 8:30 pm and we sat outside with him after dinner. It still remains one of my most favourite memories. This song reminds me him, his velvet voice and his skill with that traditional instrument. ❤️
